<br>
As Otere stood behind Yakut and watched her receive the greeting she well desirved, Otere began to feel something in the air build up.  She moved her head to face the platform and brought her eyes back into focus.  Otere had realized what feeling that was building up, and it was excitement.<br>
<br>
She turned her body in the way she was looking and began to make her way to the platform.  When Otere came mid-stage she raised her arms highly towards the sky, in an attempt to call all Amazon's attention to her.  When she had most of their attention, she began to speak.<br>
<br>
&quot;Athelfi!  This event has brought much joy, let alone excitement into my heart.  This being that a celebration shall begin!!&quot;  As the Amazons below cheered Otere threw her head back and cheered with them. <p>_.·.Øtere, §hamaness of the N¤rth.·._<br>
