<br>
The Amazon wrapped her quite opposite twin into a tight embrace, &quot;Oh by the Goddess, sister! I have missed you so!&quot; She slid from the embrace and smiled to Skylar.<br>
<br>
&quot;And how goes it my nephew?&quot;, she laughed caringly andgave him a kiss on the forehead. Yakut heard Otere's voice above the crowd and turned towards her as she spoke. When the other Amazons cheered, Yakut's face turned red from smiling too much, her cheeks began to ache but she didn't care! She had returned to her family, and home.<br>
<br>
During the celebration tonight, Yakut would reveal what al happened on her journey to Britannia...but that was for later now was the time to party! <p>-|-Queen Yakut-|-<br>
