<br>
Then, she remembered the stranger's face, and turned to look for her.  When she spotted her, she began to make her way towards her.  Suddenly, she noticed Xena speaking with her.  Otere didn't really know Xena personally like Yakut did, but she had heard many stories from Yakut about her and had met with her a few times before.  Upon reaching the two women she smiled greetingly and began to speak.<br>
